==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stewartry
<hw>Stew"art*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
overseer or superintendent.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧The
<xex>stewartry</xex> of provisions.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Tooke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The office of a steward; stewardship.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Byron.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>In Scotland, the jurisdiction of a steward; also,
the lands under such jurisdiction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stewish</ent>⟦br⟧
